room_title: Escape room "The Fed" by Locked Away Escapes in Jonesboro
room_description:
In 1969 the Federal Reserve officially removed all bills larger than the $1000 from public circulation. Convinced that the economy is booming, president Trump has decided to bring back the $1000 with his face on it. Your team has been hired by a disgruntled organization and tasked with breaking into the Fed to retrieve the printing plates and the funds before they reach the population.
A member of your team, in support of Trump, has alerted authorities of your attempt, and they will arrive shortly to apprehend you. Can you break into the most highly guarded facility in America, and succeed in your efforts, or will you fail to finish the job?
